title: The Who - 1970-02-14 Live At Leeds (corrected sequencing by }{ey
description:
This is the new expanded remaster of Live At Leeds, but in the correct order. In order to keep Tommy in one piece the encores were originally moved to disc one. I've restored them to their correct place at the end of the show and joined the chow into one continuous piece without disc fades.
